mage-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-300x300.png\" data-large-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce.png\" />One of the biggest requests we receive from our members and users alike is &#8220;I would like to use [insert payment gateway name]. Do you have an integration for it and if not can you develop it for me?&#8221; Truth be told there are a myriad of payment gateways out there, and as much as we would like to have an integration for each and every gateway available, it is just not possible to do so (yet). So, now what? You desperately want to use Paid Memberships Pro but your payment gateway is not supported. You&#8217;re stuck. Or are you? The &#8220;Woo-karound&#8221; If the payment gateway that you would like to use has a WooCommerce Integration developed for it, you&#8217;re in luck. One possible solution could be to use WooCommerce, our WooCommerce Integration and your payment gateway&#8217;s WooCommerce integration. This allows you to sell a PMPro Membership as a WooCommerce Product and let WooCommerce handle the checkout of your membership level using your payment gateway of choice. Getting Setup Below is a brief guide on how to set this up: Install and activate WooCommerce on your site. The primary WooCommerce plugin is free via the WordPress repository. Set up your chosen <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/use-woocommerce-sell-memberships-payment-gateway-choice/\">(more...)</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Travis Lima\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7479:\"<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-300x300.png\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 15px;\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-300x300.png 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-150x150.png 150w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-80x80.png 80w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-attachment-id=\"113883\" data-permalink=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-woocommerce/woocommerce-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce.png\" data-orig-size=\"600,600\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"woocommerce\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce-300x300.png\" data-large-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/woocommerce.png\" /><div class=\"lead\"><p>One of the biggest requests we receive from our members and users alike is &#8220;I would like to use [insert payment gateway name]. Do you have an integration for it and if not can you develop it for me?&#8221;<br />\n</div><hr /></p>\n<p>Truth be told there are a myriad of payment gateways out there, and as much as we would like to have an integration for each and every gateway available, it is just not possible to do so (yet). So, now what? You desperately want to use Paid Memberships Pro but your payment gateway is not supported. You&#8217;re stuck.</p>\n<h3><em>Or are you?</em></h3>\n<hr />\n<h2>The &#8220;Woo-karound&#8221;</h2>\n<p>If the payment gateway that you would like to use has a WooCommerce Integration developed for it, you&#8217;re in luck. One possible solution could be to use <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce</a>, our <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Integration</a> and your payment gateway&#8217;s WooCommerce integration. This allows you to sell a PMPro Membership as a WooCommerce Product and let WooCommerce handle the checkout of your membership level using your payment gateway of choice.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"122730\" data-permalink=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/use-woocommerce-sell-memberships-payment-gateway-choice/screen-shot-2017-10-10-at-12-02-37-pm/\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM.png\" data-orig-size=\"2484,694\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screen Shot 2017-10-10 at 12.02.37 PM\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM-300x84.png\" data-large-file=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM-1024x286.png\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-122730\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2484\" height=\"694\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM.png 2484w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM-300x84.png 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM-1024x286.png 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screen-Shot-2017-10-10-at-12.02.37-PM-1170x327.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2484px) 100vw, 2484px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Getting Setup</h2>\n<p>Below is a brief guide on how to set this up:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Install and activate <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce</a> on your site. The primary WooCommerce plugin is free via the WordPress repository.</li>\n<li>Set up your chosen payment gateway in your WooCommerce Setup. You may need to purchase a <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/woocommerce-extensions/payment-gateways/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">premium gateway extension</a> from WooCommerce.</li>\n<li>Install and activate our <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-woocommerce/\">WooCommerce Integration</a> on your site. This PMPro WooCommerce Add On is free via the WordPress repository.</li>\n<li>Set up your membership levels to be sold as Products. Have a look at the <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-woocommerce/#woomem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">&#8220;Membership Products&#8221; section of the Add On page</a> for more details.</li>\n<li>Let WooCommerce handle the checkout process instead of Paid Memberships Pro.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img class=\"wp-post-image\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/membershipproduct.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"148\" /></p>\n<div class=\"pmpro_message pmpro_alert\">Note that using the WooCommerce Integration to sell memberships as products only requires adding Membership levels with their name and (if desired) category restrictions. None of the level pricing, page setup, or payment settings are needed. If you want to handle recurring payments using this method, you will need to use WooCommerce Subscriptions along with this integration.</div>\n<hr />\n<h2>This won&#8217;t work for me. Now what?</h2>\n<p>Perhaps, this workaround is not going to work for you. If that is the case maybe some of these alternatives might do the trick!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/gateway/adding-a-new-gateway/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Adding a New Gateway documentation</a> (Warning: Not for the faint of heart!) &#8211; It is recommended that you are an experienced code wrangler if you decide to take this project on.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/developers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find a Developer to help</a>. We have some experienced WordPress/Paid Memberships Pro Partner developers that you can get in touch with that will happily give you an estimate on integrating your Payment Gateway for you. Simply <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/developers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">open up a developer request</a> and one of our developer partners will get in touch with you.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/use-woocommerce-sell-memberships-payment-gateway-choice/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"x